# 🚀 AI Application Tracking System (ATS)

### AWS + Python + Streamlit + Google Gemini AI

An **AI-powered Application Tracking System (ATS)** that analyzes resumes using **Google Gemini AI** and provides intelligent feedback.

This project demonstrates integration of:

* ☁️ **AWS EC2 (Ubuntu Server)**
* 🐍 **Python**
* 🎈 **Streamlit**
* 🤖 **Google Gemini AI (GCP)**

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# 🏗 Architecture

```
User Browser
     │
     ▼
Streamlit Web App (Port 8501)
     │
     ▼
Python ATS Application
     │
     ▼
Google Gemini AI API (GCP)
     │
     ▼
AI Resume Analysis & Feedback
```

